{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1aca887a93","title":"“五一”节和张×的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cb685ec319","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":1,"articleId":"1aca887a93","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3072f49961","type":"paragraph","text":"五一”节和张×的蓄","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d3539c1719","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年五月一日）","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3da3e792c1","type":"paragraph","text":"五月一日晚上十点三十五分在天安门城楼上，江青同志向毛主席、林副主席单独引见了张×，接见时周总理也在座。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1078151194","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席、林副主席和张×亲切握手。毛主席红光满面，种朵奕爽，身体非常健康。这是中国人民和世界人民的最大幸福","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0f94758f25","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志向毛主席，林付主席介绍说：这是国家科委张×，她们把韩光一伙打倒了，她们那里运动搞得不错。","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3047d2dfa3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说、应该祝科委同志们万寿无疆，应该就人民万寿无疆！毛主席又说：女同志也一样造反骤：你们把反革命韩光打倒了，你们夺权夺得好！接着主席又亲切地问，你现在担任什么工作张×同答说：在国家科委革命委员会工作。毛主席问：是革命委员会主任吧周总理说，也就是了吧这时，毛主席向林副主席说：她原来是个局长，和群众一起造反。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b70b3bd910","type":"paragraph","text":"对棉粮工作的指示","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"20ba6adb32","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年五月一日）","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"27d267cd1c","type":"paragraph","text":"必须把粮食抓紧，把锦花抓紧，把布正抓紧，粮油征腾工作不仅是一个经济任务，它首先是一个政治任务。一定要十分抓紧，每年-定要把收割、保管吃用（收、管、吃）抓的很紧，而且抓的及时。","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f4ba7b8242","type":"paragraph","text":"不注意储备，铺张浪费，吃光用光，这些都是错误的，都是粮食工作中的资产阶级反动路线或者是资产阶级思想的反映。","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c8da13360f","type":"paragraph","text":"关于大批判题的指示","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3bbfa1eaff","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年五月二日）","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5b6f6cd875","type":"paragraph","text":"批制文章不要象九评那样长，每篇一、二千字，不要超过三千字。一篇一个中心，一个概念，明明自白。长了就没有人看，记不住。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e73f364034","type":"paragraph","text":"e809","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":319,"end":319}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1de84e982a","type":"paragraph","text":"五月一日晚上十点三十五分在天安门城楼上，江青同志向毛主席、林副主席单独引见了张×，接见时周总理也在座。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2089841027","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：应该祝科委同志们万寿无疆，应该祝人民万寿无疆！","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5d6663f705","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席又说：女同志也一样造反嘛！你们把反革命韩光打倒了，你们夺权夺得好！","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b010dcc131","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理说：也就是了吧！","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce14ead96d","type":"paragraph","text":"接着主席又亲切地问：你现在担任什么工作？","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d0f4accc56","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席问：是革命委员会主任吧？","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e581098855","type":"title","text":"“五一”节和张×的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee768b9ecf","type":"paragraph","text":"这时，毛主席向林副主席说：她原来是个局长，和群众一起造反。","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"effd1c4154","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席、林副主席和张×亲切握手。毛主席红光满面，神采奕奕，身体非常健康。这是中国人民和世界人民的最大幸福。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f2890b3bdc","type":"paragraph","text":"张×同答说：在国家科委革命委员会工作。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6b1155b88","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志向毛主席．林付主席介绍说：这是国家科委张×，她们把韩光一伙打倒了，她们那里运动搞得不错。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"1aca887a93","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":588,"end":588}}}},"__N_SSG":true}